This is soooooo true!!<br>
<br>
Don't blame warrior for not getting enough agro; warriors have a maximum amount of agro they can generate, depending on equipment.<br>
<br>
It's up to you to make sure you don't generate too much agro. You can reduce your agro very easily. Just turn off attack.<br>
<br>
